  "excerpt": "Paella de marisco is a Spanish seafood rice dish with prawns, mussels, squid, and saffron. The rice absorbs a rich seafood stock flavoured with tomato and smoked paprika. The seafood goes in at the end so it doesn't overcook. Allow about 45 minutes from start to finish.",
